<article>
  <!-- Post Header -->
  <header class="intro-header"
    style="background-image: url('/generated/img/posts/2-12-2021-1500-1b9204a3c.jpg')">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="post-heading">
          <h1 >2021 Presidents Day Jamboree</h1>
          
          <h2 class="subheading">Mite Hockey Jamboree in St. Louis President's Day Weekend</h2>
          
          <span class="meta">Posted on February 15, 2021</span>

          <span class="time-tag-categ" style="font-size:.7em;background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.45);">

            
            <i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>&nbsp;
            21 minute read

          </span>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Post Content -->

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <p>Over President's Day Weekend we went with the Chesterfield Falcons to the Kirkwood Ice Rink to take part in the 2021 President's Day Jamboree, as well as a pair of games in Webster Groves</p>

<p>Check out some of the photos from their games.</p>

<h2>2/12/2021</h2>



